{"tid":1212743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會同法國大學交流 點講好","createTime":"2019-06-12T21:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:10:17.000Z","uid":65210,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"190cc99e5b8fc06c6848c5e547da4eecee8077f4","tid":1212743,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:28:27.000Z","msg":"6.9前已經離開咗香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住 屌細力啲 兩日都無參與到 <br />\n尋日6.12 法國全日Keep住mon post <br />\n基本上了解曬全日發生咩事 <br />\n香港嘅朋友都衝曬上前線捱打<br />\n而我無得出一份力不特止<br />\n身邊啲同學仲係玩樂 自拍 影相 打卡<br />\n真係好無力<br />\n聽日會同法國大學交流 會講有關「雨傘運動」「反送中」<br />\n自問英文唔夠好<br />\n所以希望可以有英文好嘅人幫手列Point<br />\n暫時做到嘅野只有同外國人講下咩生咩事<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備咗聯署段野簡單解釋<br />\n以及打算講雨傘 6.9百萬人和平上街如何演變成暴力衝突<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong government has proposed the Extradition Bill, which will allow them to surrender Hong Kong citizens to the People's Republic of China. If passed, Hong Kong people and all the foreigner who are residing in Hong Kong will be exposed to the risk of facing criminal proceedings in China, where there has been decade long concerns over the true implementation of the rule of law and human rights."},{"pid":"60396dbad6d081e7318c7acac8cb512d0b12ceb6","tid":1212743,"uid":157522,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:31:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTIqDFPjypU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiTIqDFPjypU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=0bcac523\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTIqDFPjypU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">法國記者</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">La France &agrave; Hong-Kong<br />\n法 國 駐 港 澳 總 領 事 館</span></span><br />\n地址:        香港 金鐘 夏愨道18號 海富中心第二座 25 - 26樓<br />\n電話總機: (+852) 3752 9900<br />\n圖文傳真: (+852) 3752 9901<br />\n電子郵件: informations@consulfrance-hongkong.org"},{"pid":"f51f45f910df39ad667e691feaf852022286465b","tid":1212743,"uid":83025,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:50:22.000Z","msg":"樓主加油！！多謝你！<br />\n可以引用唔同報紙e.g. BBC, CNN, SCMP嘅睇法 / 要點黎充實自己份稿不足嘅地方？"},{"pid":"ed2605ea593d40c7f911181d8aa8ad097f3219ae","tid":1212743,"uid":156468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:05:46.000Z","msg":"直接比佢睇法國記者條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7aa3238ecb47d7813da021780e55209ad36112","tid":1212743,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed2605ea593d40c7f911181d8aa8ad097f3219ae","tid":1212743,"uid":156468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:05:46.000Z","msg":"直接比佢睇法國記者條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5a21a20557c440a91c5a2fefa7f10d2bd00f4a","tid":1212743,"uid":19278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:23:55.000Z","msg":"仲有黑警濫權打記者，手無寸鐵嘅市民，同headshot嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c386e7c894fcf39710052bafe5b28ea5c53c4d","tid":1212743,"uid":31712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T22:25:42.000Z","msg":"同邊間大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feeaab4bcc3a22d088bec08c377270d25d0b769e","tid":1212743,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51f45f910df39ad667e691feaf852022286465b","tid":1212743,"uid":83025,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:50:22.000Z","msg":"樓主加油！！多謝你！<br />\n可以引用唔同報紙e.g. BBC, CNN, SCMP嘅睇法 / 要點黎充實自己份稿不足嘅地方？"},"c