製作&quot;犯人&quot;<br />\n話個外國遊客係中國犯咗啲乜乜事/法，然後要香港引導佢上去<br />\n估計大家都重記得北韓囚禁美國大學生瓦姆比爾拎佢嚟同侵侵講數<br />\n而且最近都有加拿大前外交官係中國被拘捕<br />\n如果香港過咗逃犯條例，咁外國就要被迫因為中國有人質係手而屈服/談判，畢竟外國民主政府要回應民眾壓力要求營救被囚國民<br />\n所以外國人/護照持有者都不能獨善其身<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74ff71c6d1fd0d1bc575f6649441a18575dccd","tid":1212743,"uid":37673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0db024356d914433068cccd3d3a0cd1816283c75","tid":1212743,"uid":53150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f660520fc875546e39733cad6011e123f87204bf","tid":1212743,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"I'm from Hong Kong, not China, not yet."},{"pid":"9780edc30113aaac6294eca1133c52e1aa5ca474","tid":1212743,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"法國仔個個都有哲學底其實唔難解釋"},{"pid":"8d76a3ddece6222615415e8665898ec69963de3e","tid":1212743,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"Point form <br />\n簡單講啲有力既例子"}]}